# Virtual environment path (a8-validate)

This project uses **`.venv`** (not `venv`). When running Python, pytest, pre-commit, or pip from the project root, use:

- `.venv/bin/pytest`
- `.venv/bin/pre-commit`
- `.venv/bin/python`
- `.venv/bin/pip`
- etc.

If a command fails with "no such file or directory: venv/bin/...", re-run using `.venv/bin/...` instead.
